description:
Remove unwanted hair quickly and easily with the As Seen on TV Beauty Trimmer. This compact cordless trimmer comes with stainless steel blades and a protective guard, and is ideal for removing hair from toes, fingers, ears and face. This pocket sized trimmer is perfect for travel and fits easily into a makeup bag, handbag or purse.
Product Features:

Delicate hair trimmer and precision eyebrow styler
Compact and cordless
Stainless steel blades with protective guard
Safe for face and sensitive areas
Pocket sized and perfect for travel
Contents: eyebrow shaper, cleaning brush, velour pouch, battery
name: As Seen On Tv Beauty Trimmer 1EA
